"{\"uid\": \"si.com-olympics-paris-games-are-just-thebeginning-uswnt-star-jaedyn-shaw\", \"noun_phrases\": [{\"sentence\": \"Arms stretched out wide, Jaedyn Shaw beamed as she danced to the edge of the pitch, leaping into the arms of her teammates on the U.S. women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s national team.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 32, \"end\": 36, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5843056706165382e-10, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arms\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 4}, {\"ngram\": \"the edge\", \"from\": 61, \"to\": 69}, {\"ngram\": \"the pitch\", \"from\": 73, \"to\": 82}, {\"ngram\": \"the arms\", \"from\": 97, \"to\": 105}, {\"ngram\": \"her teammates\", \"from\": 109, \"to\": 122}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\", \"from\": 126, \"to\": 134}, {\"ngram\": \"women\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s national team\", \"from\": 135, \"to\": 158}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A familiar San Diego crowd boomed as the teenager basked in the glory of her first USWNT goal, which came just three days after her debut with the team in October 2023.\", \"from\": 160, \"to\": 328, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 175, \"end\": 180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\", \"score\": 0.915582638051374, \"rank\": 0.09220070197924418, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\"}, {\"begin\": 243, \"end\": 248, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the teenager\", \"from\": 197, \"to\": 209}, {\"ngram\": \"the glory\", \"from\": 220, \"to\": 229}, {\"ngram\": \"her debut\", \"from\": 288, \"to\": 297}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 303, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"October\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 322}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a storybook start to the San Diego Wave star\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s international career, but it also marked a watershed moment in Shaw\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s meteoric rise.\\u00c2 Less than a year after her inaugural USWNT cap and goal, Shaw is heading to her first Olympic Games at just 19 years old.\", \"from\": 329, \"to\": 595, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 365, \"end\": 370, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\", \"score\": 0.915582638051374, \"rank\": 0.09220070197924418, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\"}, {\"begin\": 511, \"end\": 516, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 531, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5843056706165382e-10, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a storybook\", \"from\": 336, \"to\": 347}, {\"ngram\": \"start\", \"from\": 348, \"to\": 353}, {\"ngram\": \"a watershed moment\", \"from\": 426, \"to\": 444}, {\"ngram\": \"Shaw\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s meteoric rise\", \"from\": 448, \"to\": 470}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 471, \"to\": 472}, {\"ngram\": \"goal\", \"from\": 524, \"to\": 528}, {\"ngram\": \"her first Olympic Games\", \"from\": 549, \"to\": 572}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s long dreamed of representing Team USA on the world stage\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094and Shaw enters Paris not merely as a member of new coach Emma Hayes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s roster, but as the team\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 2024 leading goalscorer.\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 788, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 633, \"end\": 641, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9997756044223958, \"rank\": 0.00019492328315602107, \"text\": \"Team USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 667, \"end\": 671, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5843056706165382e-10, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}, {\"begin\": 679, \"end\": 684, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.904619835760311e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 721, \"end\": 725, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"score\": 0.9999999990777724, \"rank\": 8.839029270595845e-10, \"text\": \"Emma\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Emma_Swan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"She\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 603}, {\"ngram\": \"a member\", \"from\": 699, \"to\": 707}, {\"ngram\": \"new coach\", \"from\": 711, \"to\": 720}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s 2024 leading goalscorer\", \"from\": 751, \"to\": 787}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s going to be so cool to compete for a gold medal \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 it does not even feel real to even say that out loud.\", \"from\": 790, \"to\": 905, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a gold medal \\u00e2\\u0080\", \"from\": 835, \"to\": 850}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It means so much to me, so much to my family, being amulticultural and biracial family,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Shaw, who is the first Vietnamese-American to represent the USWNT.\\u00c2 Following a successful youth career, Shaw\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s rapid rise isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t exactly surprising, but ascending at such a velocity could be dizzying for even the most composed of players.\", \"from\": 906, \"to\": 1245, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1002, \"end\": 1006, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5843056706165382e-10, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}, {\"begin\": 1025, \"end\": 1044, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnamese_Americans\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Vietnamese-American\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnamese_Americans\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Vietnamese_Americans\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my family\", \"from\": 941, \"to\": 950}, {\"ngram\": \"amulticultural and biracial family\", \"from\": 958, \"to\": 992}, {\"ngram\": \"the USWNT.\\u00c2\", \"from\": 1058, \"to\": 1069}, {\"ngram\": \"a successful youth career\", \"from\": 1080, \"to\": 1105}, {\"ngram\": \"such a velocity\", \"from\": 1172, \"to\": 1187}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 1236, \"to\": 1243}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s why many around her act as a gravitational force, encouraging her to slow down and take in the moment.\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1357, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her act\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1278}, {\"ngram\": \"a gravitational force\", \"from\": 1282, \"to\": 1303}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1346, \"to\": 1356}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Longtime USWNT star and San Diego Wave captain Alex Morgan has been one of those guiding voices, helping Shaw zone in and maintain focus.\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1495, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1386, \"end\": 1391, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\", \"score\": 0.915582638051374, \"rank\": 0.09220070197924418, \"text\": \"Diego\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Diego\"}, {\"begin\": 1405, \"end\": 1416, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Morgan\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.3158414827897915e-61, \"text\": \"Alex Morgan\", \"types\": [\"Q937857\", \"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Morgan\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Alex_Morgan\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Longtime USWNT star\", \"from\": 1358, \"to\": 1377}, {\"ngram\": \"those guiding voices\", \"from\": 1433, \"to\": 1453}, {\"ngram\": \"focus\", \"from\": 1489, \"to\": 1494}]}, {\"sentence\": \"(Morgan will not be with the USWNT in Paris, failing to make theOlympic rosterfor the first time since 2008.\", \"from\": 1496, \"to\": 1604, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1503, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Grimes\", \"score\": 0.9999999957708496, \"rank\": 4.224658777214706e-09, \"text\": \"Morgan\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Grimes\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Morgan_Grimes\"}, {\"begin\": 1525, \"end\": 1530, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1534, \"end\": 1539, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.904619835760311e-13, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"theOlympic\", \"from\": 1557, \"to\": 1567}, {\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 1578, \"to\": 1592}]}, {\"sentence\": \")\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAlex has told me a couple times to enjoy the moment and take it in.\", \"from\": 1604, \"to\": 1678, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAlex\", \"from\": 1605, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1661}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And also just work as hard as you can,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Shaw.\\u00c2 Shaw took Morgan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s advice, making the most of those early national team call-ups to become the first USWNT player to score five goals in her first five starts.\", \"from\": 1679, \"to\": 1895, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1734, \"end\": 1738, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5843056706165382e-10, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}, {\"begin\": 1837, \"end\": 1842, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1720}, {\"ngram\": \"Shaw\", \"from\": 1726, \"to\": 1730}, {\"ngram\": \"Morgan\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s advice\", \"from\": 1743, \"to\": 1760}, {\"ngram\": \"those early national team call-ups\", \"from\": 1781, \"to\": 1815}, {\"ngram\": \"five goals\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1868}, {\"ngram\": \"her first five starts\", \"from\": 1872, \"to\": 1893}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On a team that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s notoriously difficult to break into, the historic stretch helped establish her as a near lock for the Olympics\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094in a deep attacking pool no less.\", \"from\": 1896, \"to\": 2061, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1899, \"to\": 1905}, {\"ngram\": \"the historic stretch\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1972}, {\"ngram\": \"a near lock\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2008}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094in\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2030}, {\"ngram\": \"a deep attacking pool\", \"from\": 2031, \"to\": 2052}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Talk to those around Shaw, though, and they say there is still more to come, having yet to hit her seemingly sky-high ceiling.\", \"from\": 2062, \"to\": 2188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2083, \"end\": 2087, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5843056706165382e-10, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her seemingly sky-high ceiling\", \"from\": 2157, \"to\": 2187}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s open to challenges, she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s very humble, she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s hardworking, she wants to be better,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d then-interim USWNT head coach Twila Kilgore said following April\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s SheBelieves Cup semifinal.\", \"from\": 2190, \"to\": 2385, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2303, \"end\": 2308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"USWNT\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States_women's_national_soccer_team\"}, {\"begin\": 2326, \"end\": 2333, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.036621580485889e-14, \"text\": \"Kilgore\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\"}, {\"begin\": 2359, \"end\": 2374, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SheBelieves_Cup\", \"score\": 0.9999842219429971, \"rank\": 1.5705433614524423e-05, \"text\": \"SheBelieves Cup\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SheBelieves_Cup\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/SheBelieves_Cup\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"challenges\", \"from\": 2209, \"to\": 2219}, {\"ngram\": \"she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2249}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cAnd while the world is saying, \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0098Yeah, she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s here and she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s arrived,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099 and I agree she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s doing a great job, be patient because there\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s more.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Shaw remembers talking with Kilgore a couple of days later about her remarks.\", \"from\": 2386, \"to\": 2621, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2572, \"end\": 2579, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.036621580485889e-14, \"text\": \"Kilgore\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q3918\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q2385804\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kilgore_College\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2399, \"to\": 2408}, {\"ngram\": \"she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 2446, \"to\": 2453}, {\"ngram\": \"a great job\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2503}, {\"ngram\": \"days\", \"from\": 2591, \"to\": 2595}, {\"ngram\": \"her remarks\", \"from\": 2608, \"to\": 2619}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was just basically saying we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re not jumping into anything and this isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t something that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s being forced on me and this isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t a pressure thing, this is more just relax and enjoy the moment because there is more to come.\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2853, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt\", \"from\": 2622, \"to\": 2627}, {\"ngram\": \"we\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099re\", \"from\": 2654, \"to\": 2661}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 2679, \"to\": 2687}, {\"ngram\": \"a pressure thing\", \"from\": 2760, \"to\": 2776}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2822}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This is, just like she said, scratching the surface \\u00e2\\u0080\\u00a6 There is a new chapter after this.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\\u00c2 Back in this current chapter, Shaw finds herself under the stewardship of Hayes, who is eager to turn a new leaf as she ushers in the team\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s next generation.\", \"from\": 2854, \"to\": 3109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2980, \"end\": 2984, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resour