dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the midfield\", \"from\": 3908, \"to\": 3920}, {\"ngram\": \"dynamism\", \"from\": 3929, \"to\": 3937}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s attack\", \"from\": 3941, \"to\": 3960}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She says she likes to drift centrally too, explaining matter-of-factly that it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s simply because \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cthe goal is in the middle.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Shaw\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s magnetic pull toward the back of the net is welcome, especially considering the USWNT\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s recent scoring woes.\", \"from\": 3962, \"to\": 4212, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4044}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cthe goal\", \"from\": 4060, \"to\": 4071}, {\"ngram\": \"the middle.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Shaw\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s magnetic pull\", \"from\": 4078, \"to\": 4115}, {\"ngram\": \"the back\", \"from\": 4123, \"to\": 4131}, {\"ngram\": \"the net\", \"from\": 4135, \"to\": 4142}, {\"ngram\": \"the USWNT\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s recent scoring woes\", \"from\": 4178, \"to\": 4211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cLooking in the last 10, 11 months, you look at Jaedyn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s goal contributions, her goal involvements for the national team and it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been significant,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d said Hayes after announcing the U.S. Olympic roster in June.\", \"from\": 4214, \"to\": 4431, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"11 months\", \"from\": 4241, \"to\": 4250}, {\"ngram\": \"Jaedyn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s goal contributions\", \"from\": 4264, \"to\": 4293}, {\"ngram\": \"her goal involvements\", \"from\": 4295, \"to\": 4316}, {\"ngram\": \"the national team\", \"from\": 4321, \"to\": 4338}, {\"ngram\": \"it\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4343, \"to\": 4349}, {\"ngram\": \"Hayes\", \"from\": 4376, \"to\": 4381}, {\"ngram\": \"the U.S. Olympic roster\", \"from\": 4399, \"to\": 4422}, {\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 4426, \"to\": 4430}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe is a player that can play across the front line, extremely creative.\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4507, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cShe\", \"from\": 4432, \"to\": 4438}, {\"ngram\": \"a player\", \"from\": 4442, \"to\": 4450}, {\"ngram\": \"the front line\", \"from\": 4472, \"to\": 4486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hold-up play is exceptional, no matter who she goes against, she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s so strong to keep players off of her and her ability to make a final pass or be deadly in the final third is something that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s really impressed me.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d To Hayes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s point, Shaw isn\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099tjusta goalscorer, her field vision has been praised by many, including formerWave coach Casey Stoney, who called her through ball one of the sport\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s best.\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4918, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4750, \"end\": 4754, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5843056706165382e-10, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}, {\"begin\": 4850, \"end\": 4862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Stoney\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Casey Stoney\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Stoney\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Casey_Stoney\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Hold-up play\", \"from\": 4508, \"to\": 4520}, {\"ngram\": \"players\", \"from\": 4595, \"to\": 4602}, {\"ngram\": \"her ability\", \"from\": 4618, \"to\": 4629}, {\"ngram\": \"a final pass\", \"from\": 4638, \"to\": 4650}, {\"ngram\": \"the final third\", \"from\": 4667, \"to\": 4682}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 4686, \"to\": 4695}, {\"ngram\": \"me.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d\", \"from\": 4722, \"to\": 4728}, {\"ngram\": \"Hayes\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s\", \"from\": 4732, \"to\": 4741}, {\"ngram\": \"her field vision\", \"from\": 4779, \"to\": 4795}, {\"ngram\": \"ball\", \"from\": 4886, \"to\": 4890}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a skill Shaw says she actually honed growing up playing futsal (a five-a-side game similar to soccer that\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s played indoors, typically on a hardcourt).\\u00c2 \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy futsal team played a little bit of a different formation than the traditional diamond that you would normally play in futsal,\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d says Shaw.\", \"from\": 4919, \"to\": 5226, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 4934, \"end\": 4938, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5843056706165382e-10, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}, {\"begin\": 5221, \"end\": 5225, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"score\": 0.9999999998417479, \"rank\": 1.5843056706165382e-10, \"text\": \"Shaw\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q36180\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/George_Bernard_Shaw\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s a skill\", \"from\": 4919, \"to\": 4933}, {\"ngram\": \"futsal\", \"from\": 4982, \"to\": 4988}, {\"ngram\": \"a five-a-side game\", \"from\": 4990, \"to\": 5008}, {\"ngram\": \"soccer\", \"from\": 5020, \"to\": 5026}, {\"ngram\": \"indoors\", \"from\": 5043, \"to\": 5050}, {\"ngram\"